  "title": "Digital Marketing Snr/Executive (Global Lifestyle Brand) | Up to $4500 | Central",
  "description": "<p><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Monday to Friday, 9:30 AM – 6:00 PM</p><p><strong>Salary:</strong> Up to <strong>$4,500/month</strong></p><p><strong>Location:</strong> Central<br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Plan, create, and execute engaging digital content</p></li><li><p>Develop creative concepts, visuals, and copy aligned with brand identity and campaign objectives</p></li><li><p>Track performance metrics (reach, engagement, followers, impressions, conversions) and prepare campaign reports</p></li><li><p>Support product launches, events, in-store activations, and offline campaigns through integrated digital strategies</p></li><li><p>Work with partners, licensees, retailers, and agencies to deliver brand growth initiatives</p></li><li><p>Monitor marketing and trade-related expenses</p></li><li><p>Work with finance teams on marketing administration and processes</p></li><li><p>Other duties to support Marketing Manager<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Bachelor’s Degree in Marketing, Business, Communications, or related field<br /><em>(Diploma holders with relevant experience may be considered)</em></p></li><li><p>1–3 years of experience in digital marketing / marketing<br /><em>(Fresh graduates with strong internships and portfolios are welcome)</em></p></li><li><p>Strong understanding of digital marketing strategies and social media platforms</p></li><li><p>Proficient in Microsoft Office applications<br /></p><p></p></li></ul><p>📩 Interested? Apply Now!<br /></p><p>Send your resume in to: <a href=\"mailto:admin@crew.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">admin@crew.sg</a></p><p>For a quicker reply, text us at: <a href=\"tel:91728913\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">91728913</a> or <a href=\"tel:88914996\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">88914996</a><br /></p><p>Please include your availability, notice period, and expected salary.<br /></p><p>* Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.<br /></p><p>Branson Yong</p><p>Outsourcing Team</p><p>HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd - CREW by HRnet</p><p>EA 24C2435</p>",
